import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

const layoutProps = {
  
};
export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"sprucebot-for-react"}}>{`Sprucebot for React `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="h1" props={{"href":"https://travis-ci.org/sprucelabsai/react-sprucebot"}}><MDXTag name="img" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"src":"https://travis-ci.org/sprucelabsai/react-sprucebot.svg?branch=master","alt":"Build Status"}}></MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://greenkeeper.io/"}}><MDXTag name="img" components={components} parentName="a" props={{"src":"https://badges.greenkeeper.io/sprucelabsai/react-sprucebot.svg","alt":"Greenkeeper badge"}}></MDXTag></MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"goals"}}>{`Goals`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Translate vanilla components from `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://github.com/sprucelabsai/sprucebot-heartwood"}}>{`Sprucebot Heartwood`}</MDXTag>{` into React components for use in web.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"setup"}}>{`Setup`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Follow the instructions for the workspace`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Add Storybook CLI tool globally: `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`yarn global @storybook/cli`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"running-storybook-locally"}}>{`Running Storybook locally`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`From `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`packages/react-heartwood-components`}</MDXTag>{`, run `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`yarn storybook`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`If you need to load additional stylesheets, i.e. from `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`sprucebot-heartwood`}</MDXTag>{`, you can specify them in `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`.env`}</MDXTag>{` as `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`STYLESHEETS`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"adding-stories"}}>{`Adding stories`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Any `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`.js`}</MDXTag>{` file that ends with `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="p">{`-story.js`}</MDXTag>{` will be automatically added to Storybook.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"usage-in-skills"}}>{`Usage in Skills`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Add the current prerelease version: `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`yarn add @sprucelabs/react-heartwood-components@8.x.x`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Import components:`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-js"}}>{`import { Button } from '@sprucelabs/react-heartwood-components'
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"react-docgen"}}>{`React Docgen`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`This project uses `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://github.com/reactjs/react-docgen"}}>{`React Docgen`}</MDXTag>{` via `}<MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="p" props={{"href":"https://github.com/storybooks/storybook/tree/master/addons/info"}}>{`Storybook Info Addon`}</MDXTag>{` to autogenerate documentation from Flow declarations and comments.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`To add a description to a prop, write a comment above it:`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-js"}}>{`type Props = {
    /** This is the component's title */
    title: string
}
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`This will add it to the description cell in the props table.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"contributing"}}>{`Contributing`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`TBD — This is currently a prerelease`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"deploying-storybook-as-a-static-site"}}>{`Deploying Storybook as a static site`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`TBD`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"additional-info"}}>{`Additional Info`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://dev.sprucebot.com"}}>{`Heartwood Components in Fractal`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://www.figma.com/file/I0By1hIW5Y6sEkMUKkGa9dRz/Heartwood-v1.1?node-id=2%3A19"}}>{`Heartwood Components in Figma`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul"><MDXTag name="a" components={components} parentName="li" props={{"href":"https://storybook.js.org/?"}}>{`React Storybook`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
MDXContent.isMDXComponent = true
